

1) define a class Animal that has:
- an instance variable animalName
- a constructor that instantiate animalName
- a method animalSound() that prints default animal sound

2) define a subclass Lion

3) define a subclass Cow

4) achieve polymorphism by using method overriding on animalSound(), printing the right sounds

5) define a tester class where you:
- create an Animal object
- create a Lion object
- create a Cow object
- executes the animalSound() method on all the 3 objects